# YouTube Downloader CLI Demo
Output showcase/cli_power_demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 22
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Padding 40
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Type "streamlit run app.py"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "pytest tests/test_app_basic.py"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 10s

Ctrl+C
Sleep 1s
